        <div class="solution-body">
          <div class="solution-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Solution Breakdown</h2>
            <p class="solution-text">
              This solution is to help users retain more of what they learn in
              the language learning app. It consists of an AI-powered feature
              that allows users to practice and remember words and phrases in a
              more effective way. The feature will be available as part of the
              app's premium subscription.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="solution-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Approach</h2>
            <p class="solution-text">
              We will use AI to create personalized flashcards for each user.
              These flashcards will be generated based on the user's learning
              history and preferences. The AI will also optimize the timing and
              frequency of the flashcards to maximize retention.
            </p>
            <p class="solution-text">
              The system will analyze user performance data to identify patterns
              in forgetting and retention, then use spaced repetition algorithms
              enhanced by machine learning to present words and phrases at
              optimal intervals for long-term memory formation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="solution-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Benefits</h2>
            <p class="solution-text">
              The personalized flashcards will make learning more efficient and
              enjoyable for users. They will be able to remember more of what
              they learn and progress faster in their language learning journey.
              This will increase user satisfaction and engagement with the app.
            </p>
            <p class="solution-text">Key benefits include:</p>
            <ul class="solution-text">
              <li>20-30% improvement in vocabulary retention</li>
              <li>Reduced time needed for review sessions</li>
              <li>Personalized learning experience</li>
              <li>Increased user engagement and satisfaction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="solution-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Potential Impact</h2>
            <p class="solution-text">
              By helping users retain more of what they learn, this solution can
              significantly improve the effectiveness of the language learning
              app. It can lead to higher user retention, longer subscription
              periods, and increased word-of-mouth referrals. Ultimately, it can
              contribute to the app's growth and success in the competitive
              language learning market.
            </p>
            <p class="solution-text">
              Our market research indicates that retention is the number one
              challenge for language learning apps, with most users abandoning
              their learning journey within 2-3 months. By addressing this core
              issue, we expect to see subscription retention rates improve by
              15-25%.
            </p>
